ovdata.no/for/sf/jd/xd-19620601-0001.html]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Jersey}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>[http://www.gov.je/Travel/InformationAdvice/Visitors/Pages/VisaPassport.aspx Visa and passport requirements for visitors]</ref>\n| \n|-\n|{{flag|Kaliningrad Oblast}} \n|{{yes2|eVisa}} \n| From 1 July 2019, Bulgarian citizens are eligible for eVisa access to Kalinigrad oblast for 8 days.  <ref>{{cite web |url=https://electronic-visa.kdmid.ru/klgd_country_en.html |publisher=Consular Department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation |accessdate=1 July 2019|title=The list of foreign States whose nationals can apply for e-visa}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Kosovo}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}\n| 90 days<ref>[http://www.mfa-ks.net/?page=2,158]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Russia}}\n| {{yes-no|Special authorization required}} \n| Several [[Closed city#Russia|closed cities and regions in Russia]] require special authorization.<ref>{{cite web|title=Russian Federation Country Specific Information|url=http://www.travel.state.gov/travel/cis_pa_tw/cis/cis_1006.html#entry_requirements|publisher=Bureau of Consular Affairs, U.S. Department of State|accessdate=18 November 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203003453/http://www.travel.state.gov/travel/cis_pa_tw/cis/cis_1006.html#entry_requirements|archive-date=3 December 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|South Ossetia}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}\n| Multiple entry visa to [[Russia]] and three day prior notification are required to enter South Ossetia.<ref>[http://mfa-rso.su/node/55]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mfa-rso.su/en/node/406 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015140424/http://www.mfa-rso.su/en/node/406 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Transnistria}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}\n| Registration required after 24h.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.luxlana.net/Transdniestr.html |title=Archived 