han]], [[Himachal Pradesh]]. Restricted Area Permit (RAP) required for all of [[Andaman and Nicobar Islands]] and parts of [[Sikkim]]. Some of these requirements are occasionally lifted for a year.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=IN&SECTION=VI&SUBSECTION=00&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140314003632/https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=IN&SECTION=VI&SUBSECTION=00&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |archive-date=2014-03-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://as.and.nic.in/TourismAND/TCorner/ForeignersNew.htm |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426085021/http://as.and.nic.in/TourismAND/TCorner/ForeignersNew.htm |archive-date=2012-04-26 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://arunachaltourism.com/entry_formalities.php |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701111837/http://arunachaltourism.com/entry_formalities.php |archive-date=2014-07-01 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://manipurbhawan.nic.in/entryformalities.htm |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809003009/http://manipurbhawan.nic.in/entryformalities.htm |archive-date=2011-08-09 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20190329112747/http://manipurhub.com/news/manipur/protected-area-permit-requirement-lifted-from-manipur-for-one-year/]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lakshadweeptourism.nic.in/web9.htm |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713171604/http://lakshadweeptourism.nic.in/web9.htm |archive-date=2014-07-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Iraqi Kurdistan}}\n| {{yes-no|Visa on arrival}}\n| Visa on arrival for 15 days is available at [[Erbil]] and [[Sul