oa.html|title=Indian e-Visa|publisher=Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India}}</ref>\n| 60 days\n| \n{{#section-h::Template:Transcluded sections for the visa articles|India. eVisa}}\n|-\n| {{flag|Indonesia}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=ID}}</ref>\n| 30 days\n|\n|- \n| {{flag|Iran}}\n| {{yes-no|Visa on arrival}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=IR}}</ref>\n| 30 days<ref>[http://www.tehrantimes.com/news/248428/Iran-extends-airport-visa-validity-to-30-days Iran extends airport visa validity to 30 days]</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Iraq}}\n| {{no|Visa required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=IQ}}</ref>\n| 15 days\n| \n*Visa on arrival for 15 days at [[Erbil]] and [[Sulaymaniyah]] airports valid for [[Iraqi Kurdistan]] only.\n|-\n| {{flag|Ireland}}\n| {{free|{{sort|EU|Visa not required}}}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=IE}}</ref>\n| colspan=2| \n* [[Directive 2004/38/EC on the right to move and reside freely|Freedom of movement]] \n*[[Bulgarian identity card|ID card]] valid\n|-\n| {{flag|Israel}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=IL}}</ref>\n| 3 months\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| {{free|{{sort|EU|Visa not required}}}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=IT}}</ref>\n| colspan=2| \n*[[Directive 2004/38/EC on the right to move and reside freely|Freedom of movement]] \n*[[Bulgarian identity card|ID card]] valid\n|-\n| {{flag|Jamaica}}\n| {{yes-no|Visa on arrival}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=JM}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Japan}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=JP}}</ref>\n| 90 days\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Jordan}}\n| {{yes|Free visa on arrival}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=BG|destination=JO}}</ref>\n|\n| \n*Conditions apply.<ref>[http://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_client.cgi?ExpertMode=TIDFT/JO/VI/IS/ID42022&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C]</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Kazakhstan}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationa